data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home was built in 2021 and boasts a modern, open concept design that is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening in. It comes complete with a wooden privacy fence. Other recent additions include fresh paint in the common areas, blinds, hardware and a security system. Centrally located in the heart of the home, the kitchen features sleek stainless steel appliances, ample counter space, an island, breakfast bar, and the perfect area for a coffee/beverage bar. The refrigerator, washer, and dryer will convey with the property, making your move-in process a breeze.  Located in a desirable neighborhood with easy access to local amenities as well as the bypass, the area is perfect if you commute to surrounding areas for work or play. Don't miss this opportunity to make this beautiful home your own!
